Gestalt: Multiple transformers that connect together into one robot



Draconian: Six Bots that combine together to Form a Gestalt. These following 6 bots are the ones that form Draconian. Draconian�s Weapons include a Whip for the Left Arm and a Claw on the right. Draconian can still use both his hands. Also Rock Towers Chain Guns is used as a Ranged weapon. Spinners Jump Jets Connect to the Back along with Dracos Wings. This Gestalt has no Beast Form, but with the Combined Power core the Jump Jets can propel Draconian up to 60 mph for short periods of time. About 3hours of flight before it needs to rest. Also Draconian has the Camouflage ability of Chamelon. But not the Sniper Rifle Due to his size. In a combined Height of 9 Meters tall. 





1.      Dracos: Dragon, Black Back with Red Translucent Wings, In Bot mode Wings stay out to make a Cape, Tail turns into Dual Shock Sabers. Also his breath Weapon is a Light Energy Pulse which paralyzes a Bots System for 3 Secs to allow him a second shot of an attack, Also this Attack inflicts Minor Damage to the targets Frame and Electrical Systems. In Gestalt Form Dracos Serves as the Bodies Front Half With the Head.

2.      Spinner: Bird Eating Tarantula, Black Tarantula with Jump Jets. Bot Mode the Jump jets serve as minor Thrust, Fangs Turns into 2 Daggers which inflict a Paralyzing effect. In Gestalt Form Serves as the Right Arm.(Note Allows the Gestalt to Use Fangs as two Claws Connected to the Top of the Hand)

3.      Rock Tower: Brown Bear, In Beast Mode Can travel Great Distances; Primary Attacks include Vibro Claws, Specializes in Photon Chain guns. In Gestalt Form Serves As the Back and Legs and Arms Attachment.

4.      Chamelon: Chameleon, Special Abilities include Cloaking Technologies, Uses a Cloak Shot Technique and specializes in the Energy Sniper Rifle. In Gestalt Form Connects ad the Left Leg.

5.      Chetar: Panther, Specialty Jumping, Hand to Hand Fighter, Uses Cesti as weapons, In Gestalt Form Connects as the Right Leg.

6.      Sure Shot: Scorpion, Uses Dual six shot Energy Hand Guns, Also uses a Whip that inflicts a Fluid that breaks down Hydraulic fluids. In Gestalt Form Serves as a Left Arm. (Note Allows the Gestalt to use the Tail as a whip)



Starlight: An Angel Bot, Flying Hydra Beast mode. Outer Shell Consist of an Energon Based Alloy which allows the Control of Free Based energy located in the Air to do Random effects also uses Com Signals to Hack into other Bots Processors, To read the next moves the bots are going to do. Star Lights Abilities allows her to use her powers; she is a light Combat Bot. She can only stay in a battle and her powers are limited to affect one bot at a time. She must also be able to keep the bot in her target to effectively use her abilities.




